-- Harmony Raises Wafi-Golpu Resources Estimate to 16 Million Ounces of Gold
-- Nasreen Seria
-- 2010-07-29T12:51:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/harmony-raises-wafi-golpu-resources-estimate-to-16-million-ounces-of-gold.html

          
          
             Harmony Gold Mining Co. said its
Wafi-Golpu project in Papua New Guinea contains 16 million
ounces of gold and 4.8 million metric tons of copper.  
          
          


  


        